HEADWORD: Opinionist
<hw>O*pin"ion*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>opinioniste</ets>.]</ety> <def>One fond of his own notions, or
unduly attached to his own opinions.</def>
